      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANALYZATION (4) broke well and quickly mustered speed to win over the 400m at Warragul two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at Warrnambool last start. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Winning claims. SETTLE FOR LESS (8) goes very well at this course having never missed the frame including two wins and two placings. Hit the frame latest (18.76) when third at Q Straight in a OPEN. Makes strong appeal on best. ELECTROJET (1) caught the eye when posting a flying 23.78 over 425m at Bendigo three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Should be in this for a long way. PAW ZURI (2) was in the money last time at The Meadows (30.05) in a Free For All, finishing a 1.5 lengths third. Has three wins already from this draw.",
